               <msContents>
                  <summary>Theological Treatise about the Three-Birth Controversy, Pillars of Mystery, አምስቱ፡ አዕማደ፡ ምሥጢር፡. The other part of this manuscript is to be found in EMIP 318</summary>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="11r"/><title>Theological Treatise about the Three-Birth Controversy at the time of Däjazmač Wǝbe (famous for his participation in the battle of Tabor)</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">: በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ...ተዋሕዶ፡ ሃይማኖትን፡ እንናገራለን። ይህንን ሃይማኖት፡ በደጃዝማች ውቤ፡ ጊዜ፡ አቡነ፡ ሰላማ፡ ከመንበረ፡ ማርቆስ አጽፈው፡ አስመጡት።... </incipit></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="11r" to="70v"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT1097Ammest"/>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.1"><locus from=" 11r–43r"/><title>Commentary on the Ten Commandments and Introduction to the Pillars of Mystery. </title><incipit xml:lang="gez"> በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ:...የ፭ቱ፡ አዕማደ፡ ምሥጢር፡ መቅድምን፡ ፲ሠርቱ፡ ቃላትን፡ እንናገራለን፡ ፩ዱ፡ ኢታምልኩ፡ ባዕደ፡ አምላከ:...</incipit></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.2"><locus from=" 43r–55v"/><title>Mystery of the Trinity, Mǝ śṭir Śǝllase, ምሥጢረ፡ ሥላሴ፡. </title><incipit xml:lang="gez"> በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ:... ፭ቱ፡ አዕማደ፡ ምሥጢርን፡ እንናገራለን፡ እፈቅድ እንግር፡ ፭ተ፡ ቃላተ፡ አዕማዲሃ፡ ለቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ እንዳለ፡ ጳውሎስ፡ ...</incipit></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.3"><locus from=" 55v–70v"/><title>Mystery of Incarnation, Mǝ śṭir Śǝgawe, ምሥጢረ፡ ሥጋዌ፡. </title><incipit xml:lang="gez"> በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ:... ምሥጢረ፡ ሥጋዌን፡ እንናገራለን፡ ምሥጢረ፡ ሥጋዌ፡ እንዴት፡ ነው፡ ቢሉ፡ ከዓለም፡ በፊት፡ ከዓለም፡ በኋላ፡ እግዚአብሔር ዘለዓለም:...</incipit></msItem>


                </msItem>

